OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Ken Hay
OL,5,FKen Hay, Age 98, Dorset Regiment
OL,7,FInterviewed 3 June 2023
OL,9,FArriving in Normandy five days after
OL,10,Fthe first landings, Ken Hay was among
OL,11,Fthe troops sent over as reinforcements.
OL,13,FHe said: "It was noisy, dangerous.
OL,15,F"When you have got things landing in
OL,16,Fthe fields next to you and you are
OL,17,Fgetting covered with stuff and you
OL,18,Fwonder whether the next one is going
OL,19,Fto hit you.
