OL,5,F"I was in uniform with a steel helmet
OL,6,For an operations balaclava, rifle and
OL,7,Fammunition."
OL,9,FHe was in a group advancing towards
OL,10,FHill 112 as part of the 43rd West
OL,11,FDivision.
OL,13,FOne night in July he was sent on a
OL,14,Fnight patrol to get rid of a self-
OL,15,Fpropelled gun. The soldiers included
OL,16,Fhis brother.
OL,18,F"He had promised my mother he would
OL,19,Flook after me because he was four
OL,20,Fyears older than me," he said.
