OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Ken Hay
OL,5,F"The worst bit is tracer - a white
OL,6,Fthing you can see and it's every sixth
OL,7,For seventh bullet and you are laying
OL,8,Fthere and you hear them coming past
OL,9,Fand you just pray one is not coming
OL,10,Fthis way.
OL,12,F"I was 18 and it was quite terrifying.
OL,14,F"It was the 12th SS Panzer Division we
OL,15,Fwere against and I think they had
OL,16,Fwonderful equipment and I think they
OL,17,Fhad infra-red.
